SubjectThe CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE NICOLET CHANGE OF BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval for the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE NICOLET in Quebec to change the boundaries of its district to Nicolet, Baie-du-Febvre, Odanak, St-Elphège, St-Zéphirin, La Visitation-de-Yamaska, Grand St-Esprit and Ste-Monique.
